-- Coty Said to Be Close to Deal to Buy Nail-Care Company OPI for $1 Billion
-- B y   J e f f r e y   M c C r a c k e n   a n d   S e r e n a   S a i t t o
-- 2010-11-28T21:51:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-28/coty-said-to-be-close-to-deal-to-buy-nail-care-company-opi-for-1-billion.html
Coty Inc., the seller of perfumes by
Sarah Jessica Parker and Vera Wang, is close to buying nail-care
company OPI Products Inc. for about $1 billion in cash, said two
people with knowledge of the situation.  The two closely held companies may announce the deal by
tomorrow, said the people, who asked not to be identified
because the matter is private.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeffrey McCracken in New York at 
